  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Fuel up for a day of skiing, the hotel offers a continental buffet breakfast with additional hot options each day between 7:30-10:30am.</p>
<p>The food at the Soldeu Maistre is plentiful and good quality with lots of home cuisine and a variety of traditional Catalan and Roussillon dishes being served. The buffet style dinner is served between 8pm-10pm with a good choice of dishes including soup and salads, starters, a choice of main course and a dessert buffet.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year special buffet dinners include unlimited cava and wine during dinner and a party bag for New Year.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
