  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Soldeu-Maistre Hotel is a firm favourite with our Inghams guests. Providing a warm and friendly atmosphere, this family-run hotel offers excellent value for money and is nicely furnished throughout to a high standard in local Catalan style with extensive use of attractive wood-panelling. </p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p>The Soldeu-Maistre Hotel is in ideal location in <a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">Soldeu</a> resort. Accessing the ski area also couldn't be easier as the hotel is located a short walk, 100 metres, from the main <span>Soldeu El Tarter</span> gondola, so the Grandvalira ski area is right on your doorstep. With over 210km of linked slopes, with access to Soldeu's neighbouring resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59}" title="Pas de la Casa">Pas de la Casa</a>, you won't be short of slopes to explore during your winter holiday. </p>
<h2>Relax</h2>
<p>The hotel bar and lounge is popular with guests and locals alike,  with a sunny south facing terrace it is the perfect place to unwind after a day on the slopes. When the sun has set, the bar is a focal point in resort and provides a great meeting place for a cosy night in. </p>
<h2>Unique flavours</h2>
<p>As the Principality of Andorra is located between Spain and France, its traditional food blends the flavours and tastes of both countries, making it a truly unique culinary experience. The vast array of ingredients from the sea, mountains, and farmland come together to create delicious dishes which can be sampled in the restaurant of the Hotel Soldeu Maistre.</p>
<h3>Why is this an Inghams' Choice property? </h3>
<p><strong>Family friendly</strong> - The Soldeu-Maistre Hotel is family run and accepts families and friends alike with a warm welcome. Offering excellent value for money, it is the perfect choice for you and your families ski/snowboarding holiday.</p>
<p><strong>Ideal location</strong> - Staying here, you'll have both the resort centre of Soldeu and the extensive Grandvalira ski area at your fingertips. </p>
<p><strong>Bar and restaurant</strong> - You'll have plenty of opportunities to try the local cuisine in the hotel's restaurant, or stop at the bar for a drink before heading to bed. </p>]]></description>
