  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel is in a central location just 2 minutes' walk, around 200 metres, to the main Soldeu gondola where you'll find the ski school meeting points.</p>
<p>The ski hire shop is en route just past the gondola and is Approx 200 metres away.</p>
<p>It is 20 metres to nearest bus stop for the local bus that takes you to Pas de la Casa, El Tarter and the capital Andorra la Vella.</p>]]></locationDescription>
